parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The incompatibility of the 17-inch tires and rims can cause tire blowouts, rim bending, and loss of control, leading to accidents and potential injuries.
The defective tire design can cause tire blowouts, loss of control, and accidents, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
The failure of the electronic throttle body can cause the engine to lose power, stall, or lurch forward, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or near-misses, especially on the highway.
symptoms: The engine loses power when accelerating
the engine check light comes on and off
the vehicle dies at low speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Electronic Throttle Module (ETM) can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: the vehicle has a rough or erratic idle
the throttle response is slow or delayed
the vehicle has a lack of power or acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ETC system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to drive, leading to potential accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The ETC warning light comes on while driving
the throttle body needs to be replaced.
